### Get all goals with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/goals?page=1&limit=10&status=in_progress&priority=high&category=Learning
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get goal statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/goals/statistics
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get goal statistics for specific volunteer (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/goals/statistics?volunteerId=USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Get goal categories
GET http://localhost:3000/goals/categories
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get specific goal
GET http://localhost:3000/goals/GOAL_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Update goal
PATCH http://localhost:3000/goals/GOAL_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Advanced NestJS Framework",
  "description": "Complete an advanced course on NestJS development",
  "priority": "medium",
  "progress": 50
}

### Update goal status
PATCH http://localhost:3000/goals/GOAL_ID/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Update goal progress
PATCH http://localhost:3000/goals/GOAL_ID/progress
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "progress": 75,
  "notes": "Completed chapters 1-5"
}

### Weekly processing (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/goals/weekly-processing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Process overdue goals (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/goals/process-overdue
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### Bulk update goals (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/goals/bulk/update
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goalIds": ["goal-id-1", "goal-id-2"],
  "status": "in_progress",
  "priority": "high"
}

### Delete goal (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/goals/GOAL_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN